```r
df %>%
  count(Season, word, sort = TRUE) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  bind_tf_idf(word, Season, n) %>%
  arrange(desc(tf_idf)) %>%
  head(25) %>%
  ggplot(aes(reorder(word, tf_idf), tf_idf)) +
  geom_col() +
  coord_flip() +
  xlab(NULL) + 
  ggtitle("Important Words by Season")

```

<!-- rnb-source-end -->
